name: Insomnia (itch) (eyeliekturt)
description:
A  horror game with no lore, you win by survived 7 day. In the night you try to fight aganst the monster, in the day you work by searching trash cans and sell the trashes you found

I have made a lot of games before, but this is the first project that i finished. Since  Im very inexperienced in making games, there will be a lot of bugs, error and even some grammatical mistake as english is not my native languages, so feel free to point out. It will help me improve a lot.

Peace.

P/S/ 8/12/2021 : A lot of things changed, including how monster now spawn
